title: Murphy, Mets beat Cubs 5-2 for commanding 3-0 lead in NLCS (Yahoo Sports)
text: Posts: 54,415 Murphy, Mets beat Cubs 5-2 for commanding 3-0 lead in NLCS (Yahoo Sports) CHICAGO (AP) -- Daniel Murphy homered for a record-tying fifth straight game in the postseason, sending Jacob deGrom and the New York Mets over the Chicago Cubs 5-2 on Tuesday night for a 3-0 lead in the National League Championship Series.
